title: 261: Takeaways from the Conference Championships
itunes:title: 261: Takeaways from the Conference Championships
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down their final takeaways of the season following the AFC (2:07) & NFC (11:39) title games. The guys take a deep dive into the keys inside each matchup that led to the Patriots and Eagles moving on to Super Bowl LII.
